h them.\u201d<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>How? We shift you out of the \u201cmany dreams left unfulfilled\u201d bucket and into one comprised of the increasing number of delighted auto enthusiasts who are using BorderBuddy to get their dream cars into their garages! It\u2019s remarkably simple, once you work with a trusted BorderBuddy expert, who like you, dreams in chrome. We have established relationships with auto auctions, border services, and various shipping\/carrier transports. Together with our BorderBuddy technology and industry-leading processes and protocols, we make the purchase and shipment of your classic, unique, cross-border vehicle a breeze.<\/p>\n<h3>How does it work?<\/h3>\n<p>e-Commerce has changed the game when it comes to buying most things, unique cars are one of the markets that have really flourished with the freedom of online browsing, listing and buying. Barrett-Jackson and Shiftgate, for example, boast hundreds of vehicles you won\u2019t find at your local auto dealer, catering to discerning auto aficionados, all over the world. The fun part remains, you browse, barter and buy your vehicle. BorderBuddy will assist you in quickly clearing customs in 4 simple steps:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Get a <a href=\"https:\/\/app.borderbuddy.com\/calculator2\/public\/import\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">customs quote<\/a> in no time with our patented customs calculator, always free of charge<\/li>\n<li>You send us the invoice for customs<\/li>\n<li>You pay us directly and securely<\/li>\n<li>You sit back and relax while we (efficiently) take care of your documents for import. We\u2019ll let you know when it\u2019s ready!<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>BorderBuddy has been helping cross-border buyers like you for decades. There are some <a href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/importing-cars-from-us-to-canada\/#005\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">complexities with paperwork<\/a> that we\u2019re well aware of and well-versed in, inspections and even some things to watch for when it comes to Canadian regulations vs USA regulations. We don\u2019t want you ever feeling alone or left in the dark, so if at any point, you feel unsure about anything, our BorderBuddy agents are available in minutes to take your calls (with a real, live person on the other end!) and assuage any concerns or uncertainties you may have.<\/p>\n<p>We\u2019re your buddy at the border, and before, and after. We\u2019re driven by innovation, and making dreams come true. We get the passion you have for unique, classic and exotic cars, and we specialize in getting them to you.<\/p>\n<p>Once your paperwork is ready, you can bring your vehicle or vehicles across the border, seamlessly, with all taxes prepared and paid for. You\u2019ll breeze through with all your paperwork, then it\u2019s up to you where the road takes you!<\/p>\n<p>Let\u2019s talk about how to get your driving the exotic car of your fantasies!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>You have a discerning eye and a passion for the classic, unique and even exotic, when it comes to vehicles. You are always browsing, whether in person (made possible again, yay travel!) or online. There\u2019s no shortage of ways to fall in love with your next roadster, sites like Shiftgate, and Barret-Jackson have our buying&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13,"featured_media":2804,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"_genesis_hide_title":false,"_genesis_hide_breadcrumbs":false,"_genesis_hide_singular_image":false,"_genesis_hide_footer_widgets":false,"_genesis_custom_body_class":"","_genesis_custom_post_class":"","_genesis_layout":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v22.4 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Importing exotic, classic and unique vehicles: for the discern